text: Marcel Henri Joseph de Wolf (19 September 1919 - 30 March 1999) was a French gymnast. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1919 births Category:1999 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics
